result.name: Tristar Kitchen

reviews.text: The soup is famed yet quite disappointing, not that it is bad, but not extraordinary good for this price. (hkd 82 for 1 bowl of beef noodle). Tastes a bit pile personally. The beef and noodle is good though, chewy noodle and tender beef. The tofu dish is pretty average. The drink is typical Taiwan handshake drink, hkd38.

Very delicious food! I like the fact that it was tasty but not too salty that one would feel thirsty afterwards. Fried chicken was crispy. The bar person noticed that I was having a cold. She came and offered to make my drink order from cold to hot, which was not on the menu. Such good service!!
Chicken was crispy and juicy! Full of flavor. Plenty of rice and sides. Service was quick with a spacious seating area and a view! Will def go back for lunch again!

Very nice restaurant for lunch here. Nice decorations, good food, friendly staffs.
As the restaurant located on the top floor of the building, they have an open view of Causeway Bay, and  as they have a huge windows, the nature lighting of the restaurant feel comfortable.
Food is above average, and staff very take care their customers
Broth is too sweet. And I had the spicy. Not tasty. So disappointed.

result.name: 三星台菜食堂

reviews.text: 三星牛肉麵好好味😋😋

歌手傅珮嘉開的三星台菜食堂不經不覺已經在港九新界開了買間分店，窩夫與蝦子餅日前光顧了銅鑼灣分店。

餐廳位於The L. Square的頂樓，可以一邊用餐一邊欣賞夜景。

點菜紙上的食物分成五大類，分別是好麵、好飯、好菜、好滷和好炸。

燙青菜($25)健康有營，喜歡味道豐富一點的可選肉燥青菜。

真的好蝦捲($42)一客有三條，切了片方便進食，口感彈牙。

台式排骨魯肉飯($75)的排骨不太薄也不太乾身，炸得酥香，魯肉飯的肉偏大粒，沒有太多肥肉，個人覺得可以多一點汁。

三星牛肉麵($82)有齊牛筋、牛(月展)和牛肚，全部都很有水準，放了一會才吃但麵也不會太糊，湯底香濃，有機會要試它的番茄湯和冬粉。
焢肉正！如果盛器較台化更好。

The soup is famed yet quite disappointing, not that it is bad, but not extraordinary good for this price. (hkd 82 for 1 bowl of beef noodle). Tastes a bit pile personally. The beef and noodle is good though, chewy noodle and tender beef. The tofu dish is pretty average. The drink is typical Taiwan handshake drink, hkd38.
比一些連鎖店要好，但亦非特別好食
